<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/34000362-john-addiego"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1408308996i/34000362._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
