<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/34000362-john-addiego">John Addiego</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is literary fiction in what I&apos;d call the magical realism style, and it seems like one of the best novels about multi-cultural India during and si<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is literary fiction in what I'd call the magical realism style, and it seems like one of the best novels about multi-cultural India during and since its moment of independence from the British Empire. Mostly, it's a work of rare genius and terrific humor by a master stylist.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
