<span id="freeTextContainer7086558110744414005">Life is simply too short (and this book, far too long).<br/><br/>So, Merry Christmas to myself! Robin, you <i>don&apos;t</i> have to finish reading this endless, labyrinthine <s>mess</s> tangle. Putting the book down does <i>not</i> mean it &quot;beat&quot; you. It doesn&apos;t say anything definitively bad about you, as a reader. It just means that there is limited time on this earth and other great books are calling your name. Books that don&apos;t make your eyes cross and furrow your brow in exasperation and frustration. <br/><br/>Mr. Rushdie, it&apos;s not me, </span>
