<span id="freeTextContainer12858976289731348318">WOW!!!<br/><br/>It took me 140 pages to really get &apos;hooked&apos;. Do you know there is a 32 page vocabulary list (I printed it out)--online for &quot;Midnight&apos;s Children?<br/><br/>Its worth reading this book! lol<br/><br/>UPDATE:<br/>In spirit of Sharyl&apos;s review which I read today...<br/>I&apos;m going to RAISE my my 3 stars to 5 stars!<br/><br/><br/>I read this a long time ago ---(I had to work it) --looking up tons of words. However --I thought the story was TERRIFIC!!!<br/><br/>I still think about this book...<br/><br/>so...5 stars it is!!!!!</span>
  <span id="freeText12858976289731348318" style="display:none">WOW!!!<br /><br />It took me 140 pages to really get 'hooked'. Do you know there is a 32 page vocabulary list (I printed it out)--online for "Midnight's Children?<br /><br />Its worth reading this book! lol<br /><br />UPDATE:<br />In spirit of Sharyl's review which I read today...<br />I'm going to RAISE my my 3 stars to 5 stars!<br /><br /><br />I read this a long time ago ---(I had to work it) --looking up tons of words. However --I thought the story was TERRIFIC!!!<br /><br />I still think about this book...<br /><br />so...5 stars it is!!!!!</span>
